Hi 愉快.
If you got nothing to do, just learn javascript. 

First challenge : The aim of this challenge is to change the text of body.

Mathematical way of programming :

function c(){
  document.getElementById("r").innerHTML = "Hello World :)";
}

Second challenge : The aim of this challange is to calculate the result of the computed ascii text. 

Mathematical way of programming :

function r(){
  var t = 0;
  var q = document.getElementById("r").innerHTML;
  var n = q.length; 
  for(var i = 0; i < n; i++){
    t += q.charCodeAt(i);
  }
  document.getElementById("r").innerHTML = t;
}

Third challenge : Purpuse is, with the 120 first numbers of the mathematical constant : adding pair and substract the odd.



